awards.description:
This award is available to any Lions club member who is in good standing, has all the required endorsements, and is not a previous recipient of the award. Every year a new Lion of the year will be chosen.
Lions considered for this prestigious award must have:
• demonstrated outstanding volunteer and leadership skills;
• achieved a superior record as a Lion in implementing successful service projects;
• made an identifiable contribution to the development and growth of the Lions club Program;
• achieved distinction in community or activities outside of Lions club commitments; and
• demonstrated high ethical standards and personal integrity.
